96 void iwtros::iiwaMove::_ctrl_loop(){
97  static ros::Rate r(1);
98  // ToDo: Check asynchronous spinner is required
99  ros::spinOnce();

102  geometry_msgs::PoseStamped place_pose = generatePose(0.228, -0.428, 1.2215, M_PI, 0 , M_PI/4, "iiwa_link_0");
103  geometry_msgs::PoseStamped home_pose = generatePose(0.228, -0.428, 1.3, M_PI, 0 , M_PI/4, "iiwa_link_0");
104  geometry_msgs::PoseStamped test_pose = generatePose(0.6, 0.09, 1.12, M_PI, 0 , M_PI/4 + M_PI/2, "iiwa_link_0");

106  // ready_pick_pose = true;

108  ready_pick_pose = false;
109  _accept_pose = false;
110  _sub.shutdown();
111  ROS_WARN("Moving to Pick");
112  pnpPipeLine(this->pick_pose, place_pose, 0.15);
113  home_position = true;
114  _sub = _nh.subscribe<geometry_msgs::TransformStamped>("/detected_goal", 10, boost::bind(&iiwaMove::callback, this, _1));
115  }if(home_position){
116  home_position = false;
117  ROS_WARN("Home Pose");
118  motionExecution(home_pose);
119  }
120  if(ready_pick_pose) ROS_INFO("Ready to accept the goal");
121  else{
122  ROS_WARN("Doing Nothing and I am HAPPY!");
123  }
124  ros::spinOnce();
125  r.sleep();

129 void iwtros::iiwaMove::pnpPipeLine(geometry_msgs::PoseStamped pick,
130  geometry_msgs::PoseStamped place,
131  const double offset){
132  // Go to Pick prepose (PTP)
133  pick.pose.position.z += offset;
134  motionExecution(pick);
135  this->openGripper();
136  // Go to Pick pose, ToDo: Set LIN motion
137  pick.pose.position.z -= offset;
138  motionExecution(pick);
139  this->closeGripper();
140  ros::Duration(1.0).sleep();
141  // Go to Pick Postpose, ToDo: Set LIN motion
142  pick.pose.position.z += offset;
143  motionExecution(pick);
144  // Go to Place Prepose (PTP)
145  place.pose.position.z += offset;
146  motionExecution(place);
147  // Go to Place pose, ToDo: Set LIN motion
148  place.pose.position.z -= offset;
149  motionExecution(place);
150  this->openGripper();
151  ros::Duration(0.5).sleep();
152  // Go to Place Postpose, ToDo: Set LIN motion
153  place.pose.position.z += offset;
154  motionExecution(place);
155  this->closeGripper();
156  this->ackGripper();
157 }

189  tCon.constraints[0].position_constraints[0].link_name = EE_FRAME;
